Interface Property

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface Property
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Property.
    Component of a PropertySheet, based on the java.beans.PropertyDescriptor for easy wrapping of beans in PropertySheet.
